lign=\"alignnone\" width=\"351\"]<img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/65/Judd_Apatow.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"351\" height=\"525\" /> Courtesy of Wikipedia Commons[/caption]\r\n<h2><strong>Wednesday</strong></h2>\r\nIf you are, perchance, a subterranean with an emerging writerly bent, make your way to Los Felizs leading literary star, <strong>Skylight Books</strong>. Tonight <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/372168979657771/\">the place to be</a> is amongst tomes of all types, as PEN Center supplies summer cocktails and readings with current and former Emerging Voices fellows as well as mentors for interested applicants to future fellowships. Featuring such book-loving names as <strong>Melanie Thorne</strong>, <strong>Brandon Jordan Brown</strong>, <strong>Laurie Owyang</strong> and<strong> Terrance Flynn</strong>, youre going to want to keep your ears peeled.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.anelnoath.com/partygirl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"466\" height=\"388\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Thursday</strong></h2>\r\nIf your mid-week blues have you looking to the East, head over to <strong>General Lee\'s</strong> in Chinatown, for the <strong>Catnip Club</strong>s<strong> Lucky Cat Party</strong>. Get your<strong> Catnip Club </strong>membership with ears included for <a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/product/catnip-club-membership-6-months/\">entry</a> to six months of seductive feline events. Plus, youll be partying for a good cause! A portion of all proceeds goes to <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kittybungalowcharmschool\"><strong>Kitty Bungalow-Charm School for Wayward Cats</strong></a><strong>.</strong>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"293\"]<img class=\"\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/5/4136/4786859560_7d24d5b11f_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"391\" /> Courtesy of Flickr Commons[/caption]\r\n<h2><strong>Friday</strong></h2>\r\nTake a dive into the murky waters of an evening at the <strong>Aquarium</strong>. Sure, it may be in Long Beach, but it promises to be enough of a delightful <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/469542833208750/\"><strong>Night Dive</strong></a> to merit the night drive. Take in the Aquarium after dark, when the lights go down and things start to get scintillating. Its not just the nocturnals (animal and human) who will be the focus of the evenings festvities: <a href=\"https://tickets.aquariumofpacific.org/WebStore/shop/ViewItems.aspx?Merchant=AOPNDIVE&amp;CategoryGroupExternalID=NDIVE&amp;CategoryExternalID=NDIVE\">anticipate</a> cocktails, food trucks, music from local bands, DJs spinning in the Aquariums galleries, and works of art curated by <strong>Miranda Castillo</strong>, featuring local artists such as the incredible <a href=\"http://www.squeezeart.com/\"><strong>Squeeze Art Collective</strong></a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-704\" src=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o-1024x385.png\" alt=\"10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o\" width=\"800\" height=\"301\" /></a>\r\n\r\nOr, if youre more in the mood for lashings from whips and chains than iridescent jellyfish, break out the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1586404914981260/\">leather</a> and head over to <strong>The Lash</strong> for <strong>CLUB FIST</strong>. With DJ sets, drag performance, and no cover, its the perfect way to start your weekend, subterranean-style.\r\n<h2><strong>Saturday</strong></h2>\r\nRide the white pussy over to Hollywood, for the <strong>The Catnip Club</strong>s Last Days of Disco, a lively party inspired by legendary Manhattan nightclub Studio 54. Channel your inner Debbie Harry or Grace Jones, and come ready to twist the night away to classic 70s and 80s disco with added sparkles of nu-disco and house. Period dress is encouraged: we recommend putting together an ensemble inspired by disco &amp; new wave, or go Diana Ross, pairing your cat ears with your favorite faux-fur. As capacity is limited to 300 pussy lovers, make sure you <a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/product/catnip-club-membership-6-months/)\">snag</a> your membership! Location will be announced the night of the party.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"466\"]<img class=\"\" src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/84/b3/ec/84b3ec06d0a43f96eb52f11e89363df7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"466\" height=\"530\" /> Courtesy of WhoWhatWear[/caption]\r\n<h2><strong>Sunday</strong></h2>\r\nJoin LAs favorite keyboardist-turned-DJ Mark de Clive-Lowe (MdCL) for a night of instrumental &amp; electronic <a href=\"http://www.laweekly.com/event/mark-de-clive-lowe-featuring-miguel-atwood-ferguson-5606940\">experimentation</a> at <strong>Blue Whale</strong>, with support from drummer <strong>Gene Coye</strong>, bassist <strong>Brandon Eugene Owens</strong>, <strong>Artyom Manukyan</strong>,<strong> Tylana Renga</strong> and <strong>Daphne Chen</strong> on strings, plus audio-maestro <strong>Miguel Atwood-Ferguson</strong>, vocalist <strong>Nia Andrews</strong> and beloved DJ <strong>Carlos Nino</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d4/Mark_de_Clive-Lowe_in_Ljubljana,_Slovenia_by_Jan_Prunk_(2013).JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" /> Courtesy of Wikipedia Commons[/caption]\r\n<h2><strong>Monday</strong></h2>\r\nDid Thursdays <strong>Lucky Cat Party</strong> leave you hankering for another taste of the Orient? Weve got you Japanophiles covered. Wander into any<strong> Katsuya</strong> location in Los Angeles for their featured sake sampling night on the final Monday of each month, but be sure to<a href=\"http://www.eventbrite.com/e/complimentary-sake-tasting-at-katsuya-tickets-16112131820?aff=social\"> make it official</a>. Start your week off right with a tasting of the finest Japan has to offer, with the gentle assistance of local sake experts, and all for the price of whatever you choose to tip!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-703\" src=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<i>Walk the Night is your new best friend  like Tinder without the bodily fluid exchange. We scour the web, pluck from pop cultures best and lowest-hanging fruit, and stick out afterhours til the last last call. We walk the night hard  so you dont have to.</i>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Suicide Tuesdays 6/23','','publish','open','open','','suicide-tuesdays-623','','','2015-06-23 18:02:22','2015-06-23 18:02:22','',0,'http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/?p=702',0,'post','',0),(703,5,'2015-06-23 17:31:51','2015-06-23 17:31:51','','11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o','','inherit','open','open','','11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o','','','2015-06-23 17:31:51','2015-06-23 17:31:51','',702,'http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/11203604_829445910426665_1401182518072204557_o.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(704,5,'2015-06-23 17:32:11','2015-06-23 17:32:11','','10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o','','inherit','open','open','','10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o','','','2015-06-23 17:32:11','2015-06-23 17:32:11','',702,'http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/10357645_10152850633911806_4116378722207309395_o.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(705,5,'2015-06-23 17:53:35','2015-06-23 17:53:35','','partygirl-pic','','inherit','open','