ainment-arts-33265370\">added</a> to the Oxford English Dictionary, proving once and for all that we all are perfectly content being <strong>Miley</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_714\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"261\"]<a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/9562569088_948acea9ed_o.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-714\" src=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/9562569088_948acea9ed_o-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"Courtesy of Flickr Commons\" width=\"261\" height=\"392\" /></a> Courtesy of Flickr Commons[/caption]\r\n<h2>The London Underground</h2>\r\nGood news for UK ravers! Starting September 12th, the tube will run 24 hours a day on Friday and Saturday nights.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://tfl.gov.uk/cdn/static/cms/images/nighttubemap-.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1200\" />\r\n<h2>Crush-Dab-Wait</h2>\r\nAfter recent tests revealed 83% MDMA purity in the UK (boo hoo), <strong>The Loop</strong> and <strong>Chill Welfare </strong>launched a crush-dab-wait campaign, <a href=\"https://pulseradio.net/articles/2015/06/high-purity-of-mdma-in-the-uk-prompts-crush-dab-wait-campaign\">advising</a> drug users to crush crystals of MDMA, ingest a dab of around 70 to 100mg and wait around an hour or two for the effect before taking more.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4Xqho.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"411\" height=\"759\" />\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Going-Down-Barometer.png\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-646 aligncenter\" src=\"http://walkthenight.wpengine.com/la/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Going-Down-Barometer-300x258.png\" alt=\"Going Down (Barometer)\" width=\"300\" height=\"258\" /></a></h2>\r\n<h2>The Nation</h2>\r\nThe Liverpool nightlife dinosaur will shut its doors by the end of the year.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"640\"]<img class=\"\" src=\"http://s0.geograph.org.uk/geophotos/02/22/3