m - 4am\nCliftons LA\n\nJoin Cliftons at Night with Dita Von Teese for a fully immersive New Year\'s Eve adventure to tease, tantalize and titillate all of the senses. \n\nDiscover why Cliftons has been titled a Cabinet of Curiosities. The only limit to this NYE experience is your imagination. \n\nGuests of Cliftons New Years Eve Extravaganza will be ushered into a world of refined style, luxury, glamour and excitement. At the world\'s most innovative nightlife venue you can expect Los Angeles\' finest New Year\'s celebration. Enter a world of imagination and magic. \n\nThe inaugural New Years Eve event is presented in association with LA Weekly and DAPPER DAY FOLLY and hosted by LA Legend Dita Von Teese. It is set to be an evening filled with elegance, entertainment and discovery. Guests are urged to don their Sunday best to step out in chic and sophisticated style as they ring in the new year. \n\nThis is not your standard New Years Eve party  expect to imbibe an inventive and enticing cocktail menu, experience five floors of ornate architecture and unique furnishings, and witness entertainment to tease and tantalize all the senses. Guests can expect a packed schedule of live jazz and blues music, a photo booth, and seductive burlesque performances, including the headline act by fabled Dita Von Teese herself. \n\nThe Grand Hostess Dita Von Teese requests your attendance.\n\nCliftons at Night New Years Eve Extravaganza co-hosted by LA Weekly &amp; Dapper Day Folly\n\nWith: A live performance by Dita Von Teese, burlesque, magic, surprises &amp; select complimentary cocktails.\n\nPerforming live: The Big Butter Jazz Band, The Black Top Trio\nWith Deejays: The Dapper DJ, Dave Hernandez, DJ Anduze\nWith Burlesque Tease from: Ashley Hayward, Charlotte Chau-Pech &amp; Miss Miranda\n\nDress to impress. 21 &amp; over.\n\nMake a night of it with friends  book a table. We have tables available to suit every party and budget. Book now! https://cliftonsla.tocktix.com/#/home','