/li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write previews of LA-based nightlife</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work hand-in-hand with promoters to write event listings for upcoming events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work with a team of writers and interns</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write articles about LA-based nightlife</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Review metrics and titles for clicks</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write a variety of titles for each post to review clicks</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Perks</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guestlist to events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free access to wellness classes</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free coworking for your other projects</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shares in a tech startup currently going through the first round of funding</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The opportunity to become a full-time salaried member of staff (if that works for you</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>About You: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are looking for writers with their own style who can write in a fun, sassy manner. Ideally you will have social media experience and understand how to gain clicks from article titles. You need to be aware of whats happening in LA in the current nightlife scene and have a wider interest in national and international nightlife.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>About Us</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: We are a full-service agency and events venue in the heart of Hollywood working with clients from the entertainment industries to make their event dreams come true, both within our 7000sqft space and offsite. In Jan 2016, we have launched the new area of our business, an entertainment website and supporting app dubbed the Tinder of nightlife. We aim to shake up the entertainment industry from within.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Apply</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with resume, examples of work and cover letter to Frances Vine at <a href=\"mailto:hello@possiblestorms.com\">hello@possiblestorms.com</a>.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"wtn-job\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<a id=\"photographers\"></a>\r\n<b>Photographers</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you live and breathe nightlife? Do you know your way around a camera? Would you like to get paid to slip behind the velvet curtain? We have the perfect job for you. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Walk the Night</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a brand new entertainment website and app launching in January 2016 and we need staff for content creation.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>The role would be perfect for:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A graduate of photography of filmmaking</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Party people who like to be in the club and shoot the people there</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People wanting to get in on the ground floor of a tech startup in the first round of funding</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>In this role you will:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Take amazing shots of parties and their audiences</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use research and development skills</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work hand-in-hand with promoters to shoot their events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work closely with a team of writers and interns</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Review metrics of images for clicks</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Upload edited images within 24 hours of shooting</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Perks</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guestlist to events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free access to wellness classes</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free coworking for your other projects</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free access to a fully equipped photo studio and editing suite</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shares in a tech startup currently going through the first round of funding</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The opportunity to become a full-time salaried member of staff (if that works for you)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>About You: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are looking for photographers with their own style who can shoot in a fun, stylized manner. Ideally you will have social media experience and understand how to gain clicks from certain images. You need to be aware of whats happening in LA in the current nightlife scene and have a wider interest in national and international nightlife.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>About Us</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: We are a full-service agency and events venue in the heart of Hollywood working with clients from the entertainment industries to make their event dreams come true, both within our 7000sqft space and offsite. In Jan 2016, we have launched the new area of our business, an entertainment website and supporting app dubbed the Tinder of nightlife. We aim to shake up the entertainment industry from within.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Apply</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with resume, examples of work and cover letter to Frances Vine at <a href=\"mailto:hello@possiblestorms.com\">hello@possiblestorms.com</a>.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\" el_class=\"wtn-job\" el_id=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<a id=\"acctmgr\"></a>\r\n<b>Freelance Account Manager </b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are seeking a freelance Account Manager for a role at our Hollywood office. In this role you will build a roster of clients, sell services to buyers within the entertainment industry, market to new and existing audiences, forge &amp; maintain relationships in business, and administrate a busy entertainment website with ticket selling capabilities. Salary is a retainer and a percentage, negotiable depending on experience.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>This role would be perfect for:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Any agents looking for a new challenge</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A recent graduate of a business, marketing or humanities degree</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Persons wanting to gain entertainment industry experience</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anyone wanting to get in at a startup on the ground level</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People who are self-motivated professionals</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Persons with excellent sales experience </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>In this role you will:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Drive sales to our website and app</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use research and development skills</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lean into your sales and marketing skills</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Give great customer service</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work hand-in-hand with the CEO to create a successful account strategy</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage a team of interns and freelance staff</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Successfully run a marketing campaign from end to end, using both online and offline tools</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Perks</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guestlist to events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free access to wellness classes</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shares in a tech startup currently going through the first round of funding</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The opportunity to become a full-time salaried member of staff (if that works for you)</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free coworking for your other project</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Vital Tools:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Yelp, Meet Up, Google Places, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Eventup, Location Agencies, Clients, Partners, Evenues, Cvent, Airbnb, Unique Venues, Spacefinder, Craigslist, Facebook Advertising, FB LA Mother Group, Hootsuite, Mailchimp, Press &amp; PR</span>\r\n\r\n<b>About You: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are looking for a candidate with excellent customer service, administration &amp; interpersonal skills. We want to work with someone ambitious, who sees this role as a stepping stone towards a lifelong career in sales and marketing. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>About Us</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: We are a full-service agency and events venue in the heart of Hollywood working with clients from the entertainment industries to make their event dreams come true, both within our 7000sqft space and offsite. In Jan 2016, we have launched the new area of our business, an entertainment website and supporting app dubbed the Tinder of nightlife. We aim to shake up the entertainment industry from within.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Apply</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with resume, examples of work and cover letter to Frances Vine at <a href=\"mailto:hello@possiblestorms.com\">hello@possiblestorms.com</a>.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<a id=\"designer\"></a>\r\n<b>Graphic Designer</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are seeking a freelance graphic designer for a role Hollywood offices. In this role you will: update your portfolio with commercial commissions, interface with a variety of clients, and learn how to interpret a design brief. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>This role would be perfect for:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A graduate of graphic design wanting to expand their portfolio</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>In this role you will:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Interpret client briefs</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Research and develop concepts</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage your workload as part of a busy agency</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage relationships</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Meet tight deadlines</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage deadlines</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage clients expectations</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Vital Tools:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Must be proficient designing for the web, Photoshop, Illustrator and Indesign skills required. Must be able to use Google Docs, Google Cal and email.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>About You: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are looking for a candidate with excellent customer service skills, administration &amp; interpersonal skills. We are seeking an edgy designer who is young, hungry and cutting edge. You must be just as at home designing for the web as you are designing for print. You know your fonts and many ideas to sell each product. We want to work with someone ambitious, who sees this role as a chance to learn for a lifelong career in a marketing agency. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Perks:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guestlist to events</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free access to wellness classes</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shares in a tech startup currently going through the first round of funding</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The opportunity to become a full-time salaried member of staff (if that works for you)</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Free coworking for your other projects</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>About Us</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: We are a full-service agency and events venue in the heart of Hollywood working with clients from the entertainment industries to make their event dreams come tr