ia experience and understand how to gain clicks from article titles. You need to be aware of whats happening in LA in the current nightlife scene and have a wider interest in national and international nightlife.</span>\n\n<b>About Us</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: We are a full-service agency and events venue in the heart of Hollywood working with clients from the entertainment industries to make their event dreams come true, both within our 7000sqft space and offsite. In Jan 2016, we have launched the new area of our business, an entertainment website and supporting app dubbed the Tinder of nightlife. We aim to shake up the entertainment industry from within.</span>\n\n<b>Apply</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with resume, examples of work and cover letter to Frances Vine at hello@possiblestorms.com.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"wtn-job\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<a id=\"photographers\"></a>\n<b>Photographers</b>\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do you live and breathe nightlife? Do you know your way around a camera? Would you like to get paid to slip behind the velvet curtain? We have the perfect job for you. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Walk the Night</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a brand new entertainment website and app launching in January 2016 and we need staff for content creation.</span>\n\n<strong>The role would be perfect for:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A graduate of photography of filmmaking</span></li>\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Party people who like to be in the club and shoot the people there</span></li>\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People wanting to get in on the ground floor of a tech startup in the first round of funding</span></li>\n</ul>\n<b>In this role you will:</b>\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span 